{"tid":1392481,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「你要學會如何吸引他人去支持你。」","createTime":"2019-07-31T18:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T18:20:33.000Z","uid":140337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"550daa62e34a56c361583a57f36e9715e3b323df","tid":1392481,"uid":140337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:15:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地要做既係令到更多唔支持我地既人支持我地</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然你可能會話要支持我哋嘅人一早支持左啦，但冇計，有啲中立/游移分子 就係咁「中立」，好多時要人地認同你，係靠「吸引」<br />\n點樣吸引？就簡單到好似派傳單果陣微微鞠躬已經做到<br />\n建立正面形象，文宣/傳單內容都可以用「唔好意思阻到你」<br />\n我明而家大家都好嬲好心痛<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但我地都繼續需要更多既人去支持我地架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span><br />\n你永遠唔會知道呢班人幾時會幫我地一把，甚至呢班人講少啲責備嘅說話已經好幫得手，更唔好講佢地會同我地講「我地支持你」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>重點：盡拉中立/游移派 吸引佢地支持我地，星期一至五回氣果陣，呢樣野都可以做到少少野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"aa4d90c6ff4e1ffc69cd677efedb10407cc1c3b6","tid":1392481,"uid":140337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:19:18.000Z","msg":"星期一至五可以慢慢回氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d44e05ead38695a2ebd86ab1c14f86c7e3b549","tid":1392481,"uid":140337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:19:39.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"3b980ef90e66c5d9f3491ba745c115a0fec6b028","tid":1392481,"uid":140337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:20:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e353d78eb3b10f1aee41a3c5c2a794029c8864","tid":1392481,"uid":140337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{